cs.CV, cs.RO, cs.LG, cs.GR, cs.AI

Reasoning: 
- cs.CV (Computer Vision) is the most likely category as the paper proposes a method to automatically label building roof shape types using convolutional neural networks (CNN) to extract salient feature vectors from satellite imagery and LIDAR data. 
- cs.RO (Robotics) is also likely as the paper mentions the use of small unmanned aircraft systems for navigation and safety in urban regions. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is another likely category as the paper uses supervised training sets and multiple CNN architectures for classification. 
- cs.GR (Graphics) is a possible category as the paper deals with geographic information systems (GIS) and accurate maps of terrain, roads, waterways, and building footprints and heights. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is also a possible category as the paper proposes a method for automatic classification using machine learning techniques.
